<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Parichay — Whispered Ink</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-brand">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo-wrap">
  <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Whispered Ink" class="nav-logo-img" />
  <span class="nav-logo-text">Whispered Ink</span>
</a>
      
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/poems">Kavita</a>
      <a href="/sketches">Rekhatan</a>
      <a href="/about">Parichay</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-inner">
      <p class="about-eyebrow">— माझ्याबद्दल —</p>
      <h1 class="about-hero-name">Suhani </h1>
      <p class="about-hero-sub">कवी · चित्रकार · अभियंता</p>
      <p class="about-hero-desc">"शब्दांत जे सांगता येत नाही, ते रेषांत उमटतं —<br>आणि जे रेषांत नाही, ते मनात राहतं."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-page-wrap">

    <!-- Left col -->
    <div class="about-page-left">

      <div class="about-block">
        <p class="about-block-label">Who I am</p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          मी <strong>Suhani Joyashi</strong> — महाराष्ट्रातील एक
          Computer Engineering चा विद्यार्थी,
          जो कोडच्या ओळींमध्येही कविता शोधतो.
        </p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          By day I debug code. By night I write poems that
          no one asked for — in Marathi, in Hindi, sometimes
          in the silence between two words.
        </p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          माझ्यासाठी लिखाण म्हणजे फक्त शब्द नाहीत —
          ते एक श्वास आहे. एक अनुभव आहे.
          जो कागदावर उतरला की, मन हलकं होतं.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <p class="about-block-label">The sketches</p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          जेव्हा शब्द थकतात, तेव्हा पेन्सिल बोलते.
          Mandala काढताना मन शांत होतं —
          ते एक meditation आहे माझ्यासाठी.
        </p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          Each sketch is a conversation I had with myself
          on a quiet afternoon — no rules, no audience,
          just lines finding their way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <p class="about-block-label">This space</p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          हे website म्हणजे माझं एक छोटंसं घर —
          जिथे माझ्या कविता, माझी चित्रं आणि
          माझे विचार एकत्र राहतात.
        </p>
        <p class="about-block-text">
          Built with Node.js, Express & MySQL —
          because a CS student's portfolio
          should speak both languages. 💻🖋️
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Details -->
      <div class="about-details-card">
        <div class="about-detail-row">
          <i class="ti ti-map-pin" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span class="about-detail-label">From</span>
          <span>Your Ratnagiri, Maharashtra</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-detail-row">
          <i class="ti ti-school" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span class="about-detail-label">Studying</span>
          <span>Computer Engineering · 3rd Year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-detail-row">
          <i class="ti ti-college" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span class="about-detail-label">College</span>
          <span>Vidyavardhini's College of Engineering and Technology</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-detail-row">
          <i class="ti ti-language" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span class="about-detail-label">Writes in</span>
          <span>मराठी · हिन्दी · English</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-detail-row">
          <i class="ti ti-heart" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span class="about-detail-label">Loves</span>
          <span>Poetry · Mandala · Music · Rain</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Right col -->
    <div class="about-page-right">

      <div class="about-stats-card">
        <p class="about-block-label">एका नजरेत</p>
        <div class="about-stats-grid">
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num"><%= poemCount %></span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">कविता</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num"><%= sketchCount %></span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">रेखाटने</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num"><%= totalLikes %></span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">Likes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num">2+</span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">भाषा</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-quote-card">
        <i class="ti ti-quote" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p class="about-big-quote">
          "मी अपूर्ण आहे —<br>
          पण माझ्या अपूर्णतेतच<br>
          माझी कविता आहे."
        </p>
        <span class="about-quote-attr">— Suhani</span>
      </div>

      <div class="about-links-card">
        <p class="about-block-label">Explore</p>
        <a href="/poems" class="about-link-btn">
          <i class="ti ti-feather" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          सर्व कविता वाचा
        </a>
        <a href="/sketches" class="about-link-btn">
          <i class="ti ti-brush" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          रेखाटने पाहा
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <span class="footer-left">Whispered Ink</span>
    <span class="footer-right">शब्द, रेषा आणि भावना</span>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>